Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\pos(318,325)}櫻飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「龍槍」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人所愛 被城鎮所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼光？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚六老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「龍槍」的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 那是町長發出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「龍槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:02:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒我就意味著把我送到那個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是銀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的同伴很在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妳在努力 但是能送歸我的傢伙卻在發神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這身體裡已經沒有留有銀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有留有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得礙事 就請他出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說會相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白 秋名 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在看著你準備怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為比泉的後人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做出殘酷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神在動搖哦 比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要送歸我嗎 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.60,0:05:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使用過多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實體化物體的力量在減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用潤喉糖也到極限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾 美妙的世界連一瞬也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣男人不合我胃口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺言就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管問幾次 答案都一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在櫻花飛舞中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡多管閒事的同伴是很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.64,0:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終歸對人類是不可能把道理講清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為了小姐 也有不可讓步的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是個無聊的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因櫻花開放 所以處於瀕死狀態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都不能賞花 真是不幸的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你也並沒有什麼怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要怨恨就去怨恨比泉家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我送去那個世界的比泉家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個城鎮變成妖怪的世界 你到底怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉家只留下順從於人類的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了偽善的城鎮 是用強硬的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來建立妖怪的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有礙事的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與虛偽的城鎮一起消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的土地神真是壞心眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好打一場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經極限了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬朝這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就寄希望於她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮櫻花盡染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類世界的完結
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很美妙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會讓這種事情得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言靈也已經到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試接觸一下影子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會變成完全的妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得把你們收拾之後了 理想的世界就只差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「龍槍」的力量變大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 是阻止不了櫻花開放的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要打倒向櫻花輸送妖力的你就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有比泉的技能？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你 把円神送歸到那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的共同意願 怎麼能和我的執念相比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙 被背叛 被送到那個世界的妖怪的心情是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼可能會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳作為這個偽善城鎮的頭頭 怎麼可能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這個城鎮是建立在你的犧牲上才得以建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮裡的居民並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們的執念不一樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組合招式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪和人類一樣可以合的來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候円神大人拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是靠著對人類的怨恨才活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此也是對我伸出拯救之手的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被拉入了黑暗中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那最初的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他吸引是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來的及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在円神大人的理想世界上賭上了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會照亮我的未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會後悔的 那才是正確的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睜開眼之時 櫻花會美麗的開放著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是相遇的時機不同 就變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他只是個軟弱的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為軟弱 所以逃到未知裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的龍的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吧 痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好體會我的悔恨 我的絕望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應大地的憤怒而顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起伏如觸及波瀾般驚艷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是龍脈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「龍槍」逆鱗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人所愛 被城鎮所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終之段『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 櫻花被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花…『七鄉』被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…我們要保護城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 円神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要把我送到那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮…能保護好大家的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮…靠你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是櫻真町廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因落下的花瓣 路變得很滑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家和睦共處 共同清掃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我這邊屋頂被打掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳得去和蜥蜴說說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且花瓣都把藍布壓到頭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落的時候很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且賞花用的藍布是用來鋪地上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這用來當頂棚不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是城鎮修復前的考驗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『空調』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連著的不是室外機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是沒有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫町長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉燒面超標100卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然應該點豆芽蕎麥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就要運動的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華也是 這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 樹裡說可以多吃點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花的花瓣還有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會掃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個會失去平衡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天落下的找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著修復了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的報告書你還沒有交哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點交哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也要去巡邏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
